title: Gold Player LF Duo
body:
Hey!

My name is Jamie most people know me by AusieJamster, however i have recently changed my name to Diddy Kong. I climbed to Gold V playing nothing but Support but have recently picked up Middle/Jungle as I believe it has more of an impact in the current meta. I am looking for someone to duo with while I improve my gameplay. My end goal is diamond by end of the 2019 season, however, I understand it will be a long journey so i just try to improve a little bit after each game.

If anyone would like to improve and climb with me that would be awesome! My op.gg is http://oce.op.gg/summoner/champions/userName=Diddy%20Kong

Best of Luck on the rift !

replies.body:
this guy is good and doesn't tilt at all ( I'm normally the tilted one ).{{sticker:slayer-jinx-catface}} 


great at what he does and just wants to win the game hit him up :)
I'll send u an add. r u on tonight?
I've been playing casually for a few years on and off, mainly support these days with a pinch of adc.  Playing time is usually 7-11pm Mon-Thurs AEST if that suits.
